[2026-05-18T23:22:06.309Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_bn9p9dvij3i7_2","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Browse Screen Specification\n2\t\n3\t## 1. Screen Title\n4\t\n5\t**Browse**\n6\t\n7\t---\n8\t\n9\t## 2. Purpose\n10\t\n11\tDiscovery hub linking to Cycle Tracking and Weight & Nutrition entry points. Provides quick access to two primary tracking features from a single tab-level screen.\n12\t\n13\t**Context:** Part of ShellRoute with BottomNavigationBar (4 tabs). Browse is index 1 in the bottom nav (Home=0, Browse=1, Library=2, Profile=3). Acts as a navigation aggregator for features that don't need to occupy a dedicated tab.\n14\t\n15\t---\n16\t\n17\t## 3. Route\n18\t\n19\t`/browse`\n20\t\n21\t---\n22\t\n23\t## 4. Widget Name\n24\t\n25\t`BrowseScreen`\n26\t\n27\t---\n28\t\n29\t## 5. Design Tokens\n30\t\n31\t### Colors (Light Theme)\n32\t\n33\t| Token | Hex | Usage |\n34\t|---|---|---|\n35\t| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, AppBar, primary buttons, active nav indicator |\n36\t| `lavenderLight` | `#A78BFA` | Gradient ends, secondary lavender elements |\n37\t| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n38\t| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Secondary accent, mood emoji backgrounds |\n39\t| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Success states, completed checklist items |\n40\t| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n41\t| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text |\n42\t| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions, inactive labels |\n43\t| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Borders, dividers, unselected chip borders |\n44\t| `softCoral` | `#EF4444` | Error states |\n45\t| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Bottom nav background, card surfaces |\n46\t\n47\t### Typography (Nunito — Google Fonts)\n48\t\n49\t| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n50\t|---|---|---|---|---|\n51\t| `displayLarge` | 32sp | 700 | 40sp | Hero week number display |\n52\t| `headlineMedium` | 24sp | 700 | 32sp | Section headers |\n53\t| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | 28sp | AppBar title |\n54\t| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Card titles, chip labels |\n55\t| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | 24sp | Body text, descriptions |\n56\t| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Secondary text, metadata |\n57\t| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | 20sp | Button text |\n58\t| `caption` | 12sp | 500 | 16sp | Badges, timestamps |\n59\t\n60\t### Spacing (8pt base)\n61\t\n62\t| Token | Value |\n63\t|---|---|\n64\t| `xxs` | 4dp |\n65\t| `xs` | 8dp |\n66\t| `sm` | 12dp |\n67\t| `md` | 16dp |\n68\t| `lg` | 24dp |\n69\t| `xl` | 32dp |\n70\t| `xxl` | 48dp |\n71\t\n72\t### Corner Radius\n73\t\n74\t| Token | Value |\n75\t|---|---|\n76\t| `sm` | 8dp (chips) |\n77\t| `md` | 12dp (small cards) |\n78\t| `lg` | 16dp (standard cards) |\n79\t| `pill` | 999dp (pills, avatars) |\n80\t\n81\t### Elevation\n82\t\n83\t| Token | Usage |\n84\t|---|---|---|\n85\t| `level0` | Scaffold background |\n86\t| `level1` | Cards, bottom nav |\n87\t\n88\t### Motion\n89\t\n90\t| Token | Duration | Curve |\n91\t|---|---|---|\n92\t| `durationShort` | 200ms | `Curves.easeOut` |\n93\t| `durationMedium` | 300ms | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n94\t\n95\t---\n96\t\n97\t## 6. Layout Rules\n98\t\n99\t### Scaffold Structure\n100\t\n101\t- `Scaffold` with `SingleChildScrollView` body (no CustomScrollView needed for 2 cards)\n102\t- `AppBar` with title \"Browse\", no leading, no FAB\n103\t- `BottomNavigationBar` visible (4 tabs, index 1 = Browse active)\n104\t- No FAB on Browse screen (tab screens don't have FABs)\n105\t- Safe area handling: 12dp top padding when status bar visible; bottom padding for home indicator (80dp)\n106\t\n107\t### AppBar Behavior\n108\t\n109\t- Background: Transparent blending to `lavenderTint`\n110\t- Title: \"Browse\" (SemiBold 20sp, `deepGraphite`)\n111\t- No leading button (tab screens don't have back buttons)\n112\t- No trailing icons\n113\t\n114\t### Body Layout\n115\t\n116\t- `SingleChildScrollView` as body\n117\t- `Padding` with 16dp horizontal padding\n118\t- `Column` with `mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min` containing card sections\n119\t- Section vertical spacing: 24dp between card sections\n120\t- Bottom padding: 80dp to clear bottom navigation\n121\t\n122\t### Bottom Navigation\n123\t\n124\t- 4 tabs: Home, Browse, Library, Profile\n125\t- Active indicator: pill shape with 15% opacity lavender background\n126\t- Active icon: filled, `lavenderBloom` color\n127\t- Inactive icon: outlined, `stoneGrey` color\n128\t- Touch target: 48dp minimum per tab item\n129\t- Browse tab (index 1) is active when this screen is shown\n130\t\n131\t---\n132\t\n133\t## 7. Sections\n134\t\n135\t### Section 1: Cycle Tracking Link Card\n136\t\n137\t**Description:** Tappable card that navigates to the Cycle Tracking screen. Shows cycle-related icon, title, and brief description.\n138\t\n139\t**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` with `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback\n140\t\n141\t**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding. Content in `Row` layout: icon on left, text content on right.\n142\t\n143\t**Components:**\n144\t- Card container (`morningMist` background, 16dp radius, soft shadow level1)\n145\t- Leading icon container: 48dp circular background with `lavenderBloom/15` fill, icon in `lavenderBloom`\n146\t- Icon: `Icons.calendar_month_outlined` (24sp)\n147\t- Title text: \"Cycle Tracking\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n148\t- Description text: \"Log cycles, view ovulation predictions\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n149\t- Trailing chevron: `Icons.chevron_right` in `stoneGrey`\n150\t\n151\t**Data Requirements:** None (navigation-only card)\n152\t\n153\t**Interactive Elements:**\n154\t- Tap card → `context.push('/cycle-tracking')`\n155\t- Tap feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n156\t\n157\t---\n158\t\n159\t### Section 2: Weight & Nutrition Link Card\n160\t\n161\t**Description:** Tappable card that navigates to the Weight & Nutrition screen. Shows weight-related icon, title, and brief description.\n162\t\n163\t**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` with `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback\n164\t\n165\t**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding. Content in `Row` layout: icon on left, text content on right.\n166\t\n167\t**Components:**\n168\t- Card container (`morningMist` background, 16dp radius, soft shadow level1)\n169\t- Leading icon container: 48dp circular background with `blushRose/20` fill, icon in `blushRose`\n170\t- Icon: `Icons.monitor_weight_outlined` (24sp)\n171\t- Title text: \"Weight & Nutrition\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n172\t- Description text: \"Log weight, view progress, nutrition tips\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n173\t- Trailing chevron: `Icons.chevron_right` in `stoneGrey`\n174\t\n175\t**Data Requirements:** None (navigation-only card)\n176\t\n177\t**Interactive Elements:**\n178\t- Tap card → `context.push('/weight-nutrition')`\n179\t- Tap feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n180\t\n181\t---\n182\t\n183\t## 8. Data\n184\t\n185\t### Entities Consumed on This Screen\n186\t\n187\t| Entity | Provider | Fields Used |\n188\t|---|---|---|\n189\t| None | — | This screen is purely navigational |\n190\t\n191\t### State Operations\n192\t\n193\t- **No reads** — Browse screen does not consume any providers\n194\t- **No writes** — No state modifications on this screen\n195\t\n196\t### Navigation Only\n197\t\n198\tThis screen serves as a discovery hub. All data presentation happens on the target screens (`/cycle-tracking` and `/weight-nutrition`).\n199\t\n200\t---\n201\t\n202\t## 9. Motion\n203\t\n204\t### Entry Animations\n205\t\n206\t- Screen loads with fade-in for entire body: 300ms duration, `easeOut`\n207\t- Cards may optionally use staggered entry: 100ms delay between each card, 300ms fade-in per card\n208\t\n209\t### Scroll Behavior\n210\t\n211\t- `SingleChildScrollView` enables scrolling if content exceeds viewport\n212\t- No sliver collapsing behavior (no SliverAppBar)\n213\t\n214\t### Interactive Feedback\n215\t\n216\t- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms ease-out return to 100%\n217\t- Bottom nav indicator: 200ms ease-in-out glide between tab positions\n218\t\n219\t### Anti-Motion\n220\t\n221\t- All animations respect `MediaQuery.disableAnimations`\n222\t- `prefers-reduced-motion` media query checked and honored\n223\t\n224\t---\n225\t\n226\t## 10. Accessibility\n227\t\n228\t### Semantic Labels\n229\t\n230\t| Element | Semantic Label |\n231\t|---|---|\n232\t| AppBar | `'Browse screen'` |\n233\t| Cycle Tracking card | `'Cycle Tracking, double tap to open cycle tracking screen'` |\n234\t| Weight & Nutrition card | `'Weight and Nutrition, double tap to open weight and nutrition screen'` |\n235\t| Bottom nav items | Built-in semantics from `NavigationBar` |\n236\t\n237\t### Focus Order\n238\t\n239\t1. Cycle Tracking card\n240\t2. Weight & Nutrition card\n241\t3. Bottom navigation items (Home → Browse → Library → Profile)\n242\t\n243\t### Contrast Notes\n244\t\n245\t- All text meets WCAG AA contrast (4.5:1 minimum for body, 3:1 for large text)\n246\t- `lavenderBloom` on `morningMist`: ratio ~5.2:1\n247\t- `deepGraphite` on `morningMist`: ratio ~12:1\n248\t- `stoneGrey` on `morningMist`: ratio ~4.7:1\n249\t- Active bottom nav text uses `lavenderBloom` (5.2:1), inactive uses `stoneGrey` (4.7:1)\n250\t\n251\t### Touch Target Compliance\n252\t\n253\t- All interactive elements minimum 48dp touch target\n254\t- Card touch target: full card area, minimum 48dp height\n255\t- Icon buttons (if any): 48dp minimum\n256\t\n257\t### Screen Reader Support\n258\t\n259\t- `ExcludeSemantics` on decorative chevron icons\n260\t- Cards announce as single interactive elements with combined label\n261\t\n262\t---\n263\t\n264\t## 11. Anti-Patterns\n265\t\n266\t**Do Not:**\n267\t- Add a FAB to Browse screen (tab screens don't have FABs)\n268\t- Use `CustomScrollView` with slivers (not needed for simple card list)\n269\t- Place critical actions below the thumb zone (bottom 1/3 of screen)\n270\t- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)\n271\t- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito\n272\t- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only)\n273\t- Use shadows without purpose (only soft diffused shadows on cards)\n274\t- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp\n275\t- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text\n276\t- Add more than the 2 defined link cards (Browse is a simple hub)\n277\t- Use hero animations (this is a simple push navigation)\n278\t- Skip safe area padding for notch and home indicator devices"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a83c76bf-96fc-4b7b-816c-06c2d504fe3e","uuid":"cad71db0-1d51-4b63-a091-0f6557a82e63","timestamp":"2026-05-18T23:22:06.308Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/designs/browse/SPEC.md","content":"# Browse Screen Specification\n\n## 1. Screen Title\n\n**Browse**\n\n---\n\n## 2. Purpose\n\nDiscovery hub linking to Cycle Tracking and Weight & Nutrition entry points. Provides quick access to two primary tracking features from a single tab-level screen.\n\n**Context:** Part of ShellRoute with BottomNavigationBar (4 tabs). Browse is index 1 in the bottom nav (Home=0, Browse=1, Library=2, Profile=3). Acts as a navigation aggregator for features that don't need to occupy a dedicated tab.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Route\n\n`/browse`\n\n---\n\n## 4. Widget Name\n\n`BrowseScreen`\n\n---\n\n## 5. Design Tokens\n\n### Colors (Light Theme)\n\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, AppBar, primary buttons, active nav indicator |\n| `lavenderLight` | `#A78BFA` | Gradient ends, secondary lavender elements |\n| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Secondary accent, mood emoji backgrounds |\n| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Success states, completed checklist items |\n| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text |\n| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions, inactive labels |\n| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Borders, dividers, unselected chip borders |\n| `softCoral` | `#EF4444` | Error states |\n| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Bottom nav background, card surfaces |\n\n### Typography (Nunito — Google Fonts)\n\n| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| `displayLarge` | 32sp | 700 | 40sp | Hero week number display |\n| `headlineMedium` | 24sp | 700 | 32sp | Section headers |\n| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | 28sp | AppBar title |\n| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Card titles, chip labels |\n| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | 24sp | Body text, descriptions |\n| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Secondary text, metadata |\n| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | 20sp | Button text |\n| `caption` | 12sp | 500 | 16sp | Badges, timestamps |\n\n### Spacing (8pt base)\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `xxs` | 4dp |\n| `xs` | 8dp |\n| `sm` | 12dp |\n| `md` | 16dp |\n| `lg` | 24dp |\n| `xl` | 32dp |\n| `xxl` | 48dp |\n\n### Corner Radius\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `sm` | 8dp (chips) |\n| `md` | 12dp (small cards) |\n| `lg` | 16dp (standard cards) |\n| `pill` | 999dp (pills, avatars) |\n\n### Elevation\n\n| Token | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `level0` | Scaffold background |\n| `level1` | Cards, bottom nav |\n\n### Motion\n\n| Token | Duration | Curve |\n|---|---|---|\n| `durationShort` | 200ms | `Curves.easeOut` |\n| `durationMedium` | 300ms | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Layout Rules\n\n### Scaffold Structure\n\n- `Scaffold` with `SingleChildScrollView` body (no CustomScrollView needed for 2 cards)\n- `AppBar` with title \"Browse\", no leading, no FAB\n- `BottomNavigationBar` visible (4 tabs, index 1 = Browse active)\n- No FAB on Browse screen (tab screens don't have FABs)\n- Safe area handling: 12dp top padding when status bar visible; bottom padding for home indicator (80dp)\n\n### AppBar Behavior\n\n- Background: Transparent blending to `lavenderTint`\n- Title: \"Browse\" (SemiBold 20sp, `deepGraphite`)\n- No leading button (tab screens don't have back buttons)\n- No trailing icons\n\n### Body Layout\n\n- `SingleChildScrollView` as body\n- `Padding` with 16dp horizontal padding\n- `Column` with `mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min` containing card sections\n- Section vertical spacing: 24dp between card sections\n- Bottom padding: 80dp to clear bottom navigation\n\n### Bottom Navigation\n\n- 4 tabs: Home, Browse, Library, Profile\n- Active indicator: pill shape with 15% opacity lavender background\n- Active icon: filled, `lavenderBloom` color\n- Inactive icon: outlined, `stoneGrey` color\n- Touch target: 48dp minimum per tab item\n- Browse tab (index 1) is active when this screen is shown\n\n---\n\n## 7. Sections\n\n### Section 1: Cycle Tracking Link Card\n\n**Description:** Tappable card that navigates to the Cycle Tracking screen. Shows cycle-related icon, title, and brief description.\n\n**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` with `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback\n\n**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding. Content in `Row` layout: icon on left, text content on right.\n\n**Components:**\n- Card container (`morningMist` background, 16dp radius, soft shadow level1)\n- Leading icon container: 48dp circular background with `lavenderBloom/15` fill, icon in `lavenderBloom`\n- Icon: `Icons.calendar_month_outlined` (24sp)\n- Title text: \"Cycle Tracking\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n- Description text: \"Log cycles, view ovulation predictions\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n- Trailing chevron: `Icons.chevron_right` in `stoneGrey`\n\n**Data Requirements:** None (navigation-only card)\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap card → `context.push('/cycle-tracking')`\n- Tap feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n\n---\n\n### Section 2: Weight & Nutrition Link Card\n\n**Description:** Tappable card that navigates to the Weight & Nutrition screen. Shows weight-related icon, title, and brief description.\n\n**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` with `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback\n\n**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding. Content in `Row` layout: icon on left, text content on right.\n\n**Components:**\n- Card container (`morningMist` background, 16dp radius, soft shadow level1)\n- Leading icon container: 48dp circular background with `blushRose/20` fill, icon in `blushRose`\n- Icon: `Icons.monitor_weight_outlined` (24sp)\n- Title text: \"Weight & Nutrition\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n- Description text: \"Log weight, view progress, nutrition tips\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n- Trailing chevron: `Icons.chevron_right` in `stoneGrey`\n\n**Data Requirements:** None (navigation-only card)\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap card → `context.push('/weight-nutrition')`\n- Tap feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n\n---\n\n## 8. Data\n\n### Entities Consumed on This Screen\n\n| Entity | Provider | Fields Used |\n|---|---|---|\n| None | — | This screen is purely navigational |\n\n### State Operations\n\n- **No reads** — Browse screen does not consume any providers\n- **No writes** — No state modifications on this screen\n\n### Navigation Only\n\nThis screen serves as a discovery hub. All data presentation happens on the target screens (`/cycle-tracking` and `/weight-nutrition`).\n\n---\n\n## 9. Motion\n\n### Entry Animations\n\n- Screen loads with fade-in for entire body: 300ms duration, `easeOut`\n- Cards may optionally use staggered entry: 100ms delay between each card, 300ms fade-in per card\n\n### Scroll Behavior\n\n- `SingleChildScrollView` enables scrolling if content exceeds viewport\n- No sliver collapsing behavior (no SliverAppBar)\n\n### Interactive Feedback\n\n- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms ease-out return to 100%\n- Bottom nav indicator: 200ms ease-in-out glide between tab positions\n\n### Anti-Motion\n\n- All animations respect `MediaQuery.disableAnimations`\n- `prefers-reduced-motion` media query checked and honored\n\n---\n\n## 10. Accessibility\n\n### Semantic Labels\n\n| Element | Semantic Label |\n|---|---|\n| AppBar | `'Browse screen'` |\n| Cycle Tracking card | `'Cycle Tracking, double tap to open cycle tracking screen'` |\n| Weight & Nutrition card | `'Weight and Nutrition, double tap to open weight and nutrition screen'` |\n| Bottom nav items | Built-in semantics from `NavigationBar` |\n\n### Focus Order\n\n1. Cycle Tracking card\n2. Weight & Nutrition card\n3. Bottom navigation items (Home → Browse → Library → Profile)\n\n### Contrast Notes\n\n- All text meets WCAG AA contrast (4.5:1 minimum for body, 3:1 for large text)\n- `lavenderBloom` on `morningMist`: ratio ~5.2:1\n- `deepGraphite` on `morningMist`: ratio ~12:1\n- `stoneGrey` on `morningMist`: ratio ~4.7:1\n- Active bottom nav text uses `lavenderBloom` (5.2:1), inactive uses `stoneGrey` (4.7:1)\n\n### Touch Target Compliance\n\n- All interactive elements minimum 48dp touch target\n- Card touch target: full card area, minimum 48dp height\n- Icon buttons (if any): 48dp minimum\n\n### Screen Reader Support\n\n- `ExcludeSemantics` on decorative chevron icons\n- Cards announce as single interactive elements with combined label\n\n---\n\n## 11. Anti-Patterns\n\n**Do Not:**\n- Add a FAB to Browse screen (tab screens don't have FABs)\n- Use `CustomScrollView` with slivers (not needed for simple card list)\n- Place critical actions below the thumb zone (bottom 1/3 of screen)\n- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)\n- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito\n- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only)\n- Use shadows without purpose (only soft diffused shadows on cards)\n- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp\n- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text\n- Add more than the 2 defined link cards (Browse is a simple hub)\n- Use hero animations (this is a simple push navigation)\n- Skip safe area padding for notch and home indicator devices","numLines":278,"startLine":1,"totalLines":278}}}
